OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe night
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with scattered showers,
OL,7,Fthese becoming frequent and merging
OL,8,Finto longer periods of rain at times.
OL,9,FBecoming less frequent towards morning
OL,10,Fwith a few clearer spells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells will
OL,13,Fincrease form the morning. These will
OL,14,Fbe interspersed with the occasional
OL,15,Fshower. Staying driest towards
OL,16,FInverness and Nairn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
