OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain spreading northeast on
OL,7,FSaturday. Rain Sunday morning,
OL,8,Fbecoming heavy and windy for a time,
OL,9,Fshowers later. Bright spells and
OL,10,Fscattered showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
